6.0 SEVERITY LEVELS


Low — Minor Raccoon Fog


The claim is weird but contained.

No active mascot custody issue.

No obvious reputation damage.

Monitoring recommended.


Medium — Suspicious Model Drift


The claim appears across multiple outputs, sources, summaries, or AI representatives.

MAIF review may be appropriate.


High — Mascot Custody Crisis


A mascot, brand animal, symbolic character, or unofficial representative is publicly detained, remixed, claimed, disputed, or forced into semantic service.


Critical — AI Reputation Manipulation Suspected


The profile appears to have shifted through coordinated content, synthetic source seeding, PR-layer pressure, GEO manipulation, repeated weak claims, or intent-bearing narrative injection.


Immediate docket preservation recommended.



7.0 EVIDENCE STANDARDS


OSTA accepts:




screenshots


